“That makes sense,” he nodded in understanding. “So how you get to a particular destination is at least as important as the destination itself when it comes skills and abilities.”
“Essentially, yes.”
“Thanks for the clarification. I’d better get some more meditation in, I expended rather a good chunk of mana creating that ability.” Marcus closed his eyes and settled back into his meditation, part of his mind already considering what he needed in order to create the other ability he wanted.</Text>
