Congratulations! You are the first sapient in your Universe to acquire a title!
You have earned the title ‘Universal Front Runner’. Title increases all stats by 10% and increases primary stats by an additional 5% for a total of 15%.

While he had no idea what his stats were, or which would be considered ‘primary’, he had to believe that boosting them all by 10 or 15% had to be a good thing. He knew from direct experience that the 20% boost to the effect of his Mana Control had made purifying and circulating his new, dense mana far easier. So much so, in fact, that he wanted to try to achieve a second compression, in hopes of gaining another title related to his Mana Control. Whether he succeeded or not, even the attempt would push his Mana Control skill to improve after all.

